blueprint_book.label: Space Exploration (v0.5)
blueprint_book.description:
Blueprints for Space Exploration games that use the "self building" system from my self-building-factory:
https://factorioprints.com/view/-MNZWdWosuqr3vtaC2hD

These cover a lot of the planetside work but the "space" aspect will generally be omitted because:
 - I don't want to spoil it.
 - I don't use automated construction trains in space.

V 0.5:
* Added Belt q-block.
* Fixed some loaders in Basic Science (should be red).
* Added solid fuel to Mall (mostly so doesn't stall from full methane).
